name: FemboyClicker(Alpha)
description: (PC only) This is a game, where you gain cuteness that you can later sell for money! There's not much to it now, just a few things you can do basically. The game is still in development and I just wanted to post this here. I would be so glad if you reported any bugs or glitches while playing! I'm planning to add sprites and sound effects for a better appearance too. I'm not planning much with this game, I'm still learning and my goal is to finish the game rather than advertise it and reach more players. Also! I don't expect any financial income so please don't send me anything unless you really reaaallly want to.
